'''Dado Colletti''', magaca dhabta ah '''Riccardo Broccoletti''' (wuxuu ku dhashay 27 Ogosto 1974 [[Roma]]), waa jilaa filim Talyaani ah, jilaa cod, iyo soo-bandhig raadiyaha iyo telefishinka.

